 Rule 3: Detect PowerShell encoded command

=============================
<rule id="100102" level="10">
  <if_sid>61603</if_sid>
  <match>powershell.exe</match>
  <regex>-enc|-EncodedCommand</regex>
  <description>Suspicious PowerShell encoded command</description>
</rule>
